Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,每次...每次飛奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不顧自己的船的艦長 世界上那裡會有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,海上的同伴 不是一家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這艘船上的船員 不是一家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:02.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我果然 做為艦長失職了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,回收完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:17.94,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這樣一身濕 會感冒的哦 去泡個浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,畢竟是艦長 我就知道她會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,勝田同學 現在位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,逃跑時 都盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有時間去 確認位置的空閒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,回報損傷情況及確認周邊狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,前方 什麽都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左舷 什麽都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,右舷 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雷達一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,無法接收信號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,聲納 什麽都聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不要異口同聲說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,似乎電子裝備 全部故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是壞掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好像受到 不明電磁波干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我在觀測星空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,開始天文觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現在的位置 出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,北緯 35度 15分29秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:25.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,東経 136度 4分35秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們現在...呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那個 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,報告現況 要及時準確
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在琵琶湖的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我們在琵琶湖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是啊 現在可以通到裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,難怪 會這麼風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們重新再觀測一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,出了一身臭汗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好想 趕快洗個澡 清爽 清爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 現在是輪機組 洗澡的時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:05.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,身為一艦之長 不遵規定 我覺得不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怎麽 怎麽 在吵什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:15.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 啊咧 你全身都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,非常時期 還說什麼 規矩不規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,趕快進去來洗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你們也不要在那裡看著 趕快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:29.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,東舞鶴學校的教員艦 因武藏號的攻擊而失去航行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,果然 是學生的叛亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,如果是真的叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,萬一 武藏號來到浮舟都市的話 能擋得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,根據 晴風的報告 飛彈對她們無效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,能用魚雷飽和或者火炮集中攻擊 制止她們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:48.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號聚集了 成績優秀的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有導引的魚雷 在射程外命中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:51.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有那麼容易？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是很難呢 若是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,只能用同等的戰鬥力來對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,用18吋對抗18吋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:04.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但吳市的大和號及舞鶴的信濃號 目前都在入塢保養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那佐世保的紀伊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:09.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不行 目前遠洋航行中 在地球的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,16吋 14吋等炮無法與其較量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:19.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這次的主砲從5吋變成了3.9吋對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:22.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,5吋也有5吋的優點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過這點 真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好想在我的船上也裝個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,用6萬馬力燒出來晴風艦 自豪的洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過維護它 挺幸苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,經常會鬧脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,對...對 到頭來輸出功率下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,高壓鍋爐 就失去意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,而且艦橋隨時 叫我們開全速呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:46.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我說艦長 上面是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們燒火的 完全不知道外面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不趁現在問就問不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我想想 東舞鶴學校的教員艦與武藏號交戰...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號是 我們學校那艘？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,東舞鶴學校 是之前那潛水艇的學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,教員艦 想必是最新銳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但我們也被老師攻擊過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,兩者是相同情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,所以想前去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,身為艦長 她卻還是飛奔了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小艇一艘 能阻止得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明明 另外有更適合擔任艦長的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:25.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以前就講過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,上頭的人 又輕率又笨才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左舷 肋骨編號135號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,吃水線附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,發現了20cm×50cm的破口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,確認到 少量重油的洩漏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,損傷 相當嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,很舒服的泡浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你很擔心武藏號對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號的艦長是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是我從小的玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號上 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要如何 才能幫到她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,擔心 別人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,照顧好自己的船 才是重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,說不定 與我的艦長一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:25.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,武藏號的艦長 或許也是試圖獨自守護艦船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我的艦長 緹雅...她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:39.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,總是能快速做出判斷 並堅決行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是位出色的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:44.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,若艦長緊不安慮 艦內所有人都會不安焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:49.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,所以艦長她 總是將她的不安隱藏於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,她曾說過 會獨自背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我並非如此出色的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你不是救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現在能夠站在這裡 我是感謝你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:09.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,連曾經總是逃避的我 都想要加把勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 能打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:34.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,從剛剛開始 就收不到訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但從艦內接收到微弱電波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不是手機發出的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我想不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那有確認的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,帶我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小白...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副艦長 之後拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣 就可以探測出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:01.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,測不出來 那種東西怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,哎呀 有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:16.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那是 美波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,五十六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好小 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:36.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,五十六 好厲害呢 抓到老鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,啊咧 顏色有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,別碰牠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那不是老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,通信恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雷達恢復正常了 這樣一來可以搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,周邊的聲音 能聽起來 清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,看來 牠就是罪魁禍首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,牠的基因 與老鼠有些差異不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,而且還感染了 奇怪的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:06.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,炮術長的血液中 也被檢測到這種病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,炮術長失去理智 電子裝備故障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,可能 都是它搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:19.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,只要研究一下牠的話 就能救回同學們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,五十六好厲害 是你的功勞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今天起 就叫你提督吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大提督？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,隨便改些提督之類的名字不合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,再說向學校報告 才是首要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,前方 發現漂浮物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.86,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像在雲上面那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.82,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不過周圍有水雷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,用東西捅它 不怕爆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在近處的是 老舊的觸發式水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不去按凸起部分 就不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全部引爆了不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,霧不散去 則不知道周圍有多少水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,引爆其中一個 引起連鎖爆炸很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,昨夜 我用聲納主動式 對周邊探測
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,範圍有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大概是 以阻塞航路為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,相對範圍較小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,被佈置的水雷 類型不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,考慮到水深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:40.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我想是 錨雷 海底錨雷 沉底水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,錨雷是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以鋼索連著 撞上了就會砰砰聲爆炸那種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有必要進行掃雷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,掃雷的程序是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,首先 用掃雷索 連接各種掃雷具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,然後將部署器 投入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:04.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,伴隨船的前進 部署器向左右延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.41,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沉降器 在艦艉給拖曳著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,水雷的鋼鎖 勾到掃雷索的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:15.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就會一直移動 切斷器會哢嚓地切斷它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,然後用機槍 對浮起來的水雷砰砰砰地射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那是輪到我出場了 快讓我射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,如今 周圍被水雷包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,無法開船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有...掃雷具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雖然 沒有裝備正式的掃雷具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但必須盡我們所能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,人工水下排雷 很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,用小艇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,確實那個由於很小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,聲音 水壓 磁力等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,觸發各種水雷的可能性較低
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為小艇乘員 裝備通常的配備外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,再加上 雙重安全器具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 請不要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,啊咧 明娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,納豆 不符合你口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:13.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不 沒有那回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:13.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,咬舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,咬舌頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,其實 日本料理 吃不習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,未能察覺到 抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那今天 就做德國菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不用 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不要緊 我很擅長做德国菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那今天決定 做德國菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,修理完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,周邊水雷的情況 也確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,準備掃雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:53.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,畢竟掃雷 是為了安全航行中 重要的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,首先處理 視線範圍內的水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,耶 終於到我們出場了 走吧 志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,快感 手感 成吉思汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,給它取個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,因為是海豹 就叫小摩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那樣好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:28.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過這水雷會是誰佈置的 很危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:32.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是過去被佈置的水雷 跨越時代復活過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:35.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,消失在馬尾藻海的水雷 居然出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這一定是某國的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,陰謀...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:45.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這一帶的水雷 應該是各國為了 保護本國的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以及防衛海外交通航線 而佈置的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,20世紀初的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現實一點 也不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,戰爭發生的話 就不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為了避免戰爭發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,超越國界 保護海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,藍色人魚 才被設立的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,藍色人魚的主要任務是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:07.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救援 掃雷及護航航線的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,生於海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,守護海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,走向...海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這就是藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要十分注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,展開完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,開始掃雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,別開得太快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小理 浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好 來大幹一場...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,剛才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,前方發生 水下爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,波及到小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,收到救難信號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有兩個信號反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是緊急裝置發出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要去救她們才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 你又打算擅離職守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但...是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 一起來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副艦長 之後拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,呃...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副艦長 之後交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全員 一切以本艦安全為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,萬里小路同學 偵測一下 還有沒有其他水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長應該留在艦橋指揮 才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,Always on the deck這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不就 這個意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:58.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,岬同學 認同了一直再逃避的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:04.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我完全 不懂理想的艦長 是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:08.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但是 我們的艦長 是岬同學太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,謝謝 小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,啊咧 我發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我去掃雷了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:30.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,對哦 這是安全裝置內部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小理...小理在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有人會來救我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,一定...會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小代 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:55.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,捉住我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救援成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那個 說起德國料理 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,德國豬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯 這是北方的菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們那裡是烤豬腳...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:36.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,一般來說 都是用烤的比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:40.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那 那下一道菜是必吃的 德國爽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是德國酸菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你那個是 醋醃製的卷心菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,其實 用乳酸發酵的才是正宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,下一道菜 是吉列
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是炸豬排對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,吉列是德國菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,哦 是炸豬扒對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:01.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在我們國家 不會切得這麼厚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那麼 這是壓軸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯 說起德國料理 果然還是漢堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這是肉丸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這是德國 不怎麼常見的菜式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,相比之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這個蒸過的馬鈴薯和大鍋菜 看來很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:21.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我要是有德國香腸的話 在海上就毫無怨言了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這是誰做的
